description.p:
In another aspect, the above-described compositions include the following compounds or a derivative thereof; said derivative being selected from the group consisting of pharmaceutically acceptable salts and esters with lower alkanols:

N,N-dichloro-2,2-dimethyltaurine;
N,N-dichloro-1,1,2,2-tetramethyltaurine;
N,N-dibromo-2,2-dimethyltaurine;
N,N-dibromo-1,1,2,2-tetramethyltaurine;
N,N-dichloro-3,3-dimethylhomotaurine;
or a pharmaceutically acceptable salt or ester with C1-C6 alkanols.
